Return to the Table of Contents

Scope and Content

Records and resource files of the NCUEA; consisting of papers of Geno Baroni, John Kromkowski and other NCUEA directors and staff members; correspondence, ledgers, financial records, manuscripts, curricula vitae, interviews, clippings, photocopies, mimeographed material, government publications, and other printed material; having to do with projects funded by government grants, and with topics of interest to NCUEA, including domestic and foreign ethnic issues.
